# Table Component

Tables display data in rows and columns.

## Usage

```html
<table class="table">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Column 1</th>
      <th>Column 2</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>Row 1 Col 1</td>
      <td>Row 1 Col 2</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
```

