## Variants

### Striped

```html
<table class="table table-striped">
  ...
</table>
```

### Hover

```html
<table class="table table-hover">
  ...
</table>
```

## Accessibility Notes

- Use `<thead>`, `<tbody>`, `<tfoot>`, `<tr>`, `<th>`, and `<td>` semantically.
- Provide headers for columns with `<th scope="col">`.
- For complex tables, include `scope` or `headers` attributes to associate cells and headers. 